@node "reqs" "Requirements"

                             **********************
                             *    REQUIREMENTS    *
                             **********************


HardWare:

  *Amiga 1200
  *68020 or higher
  *HardDrive Recommended
  *2 MB RAM

Software:
  *MUI 3.8 or passibly lower
  *TextEditor.mcc
  *TearOff.mcc
  *CompactWindow.mcc
  *TWFmultiLED.mcc
  *AmigaOS 3 or possibly lower
  *openurl.library (optional)
@endnode

